2 1st Session of the 60th Legislature (2025)
4
5
6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to appropriations; making
appropriation to the State Department of Education;
8 stating amount and purpose; requiring promulgation of
rules; providing an effective date; and declaring an
9 emergency.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the State Department
14 of Education from any monies not otherwise appropriated from the
15 General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal year
16 ending June 30, 2026, the sum of Twelve Million Dollars
17 ($12,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to expand
18 the School Counselor Corps program. The State Department of
19 Education shall promulgate rules necessary to restore or expand the
20 School Counselor Corps program.
21 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
22 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
23 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
